Improved by: @Ivandrofly

00:25.305 --> 00:27.272
Brain damage
sustained on the front lines...

00:27.274 --> 00:29.941
You have to understand...

00:29.943 --> 00:33.145
that Taiwan is part
and parcel of China.

00:33.147 --> 00:35.914
