00:37.550 --> 00:40.719
There is no
choice between austerity and growth.

00:42.755 --> 00:45.390
Man Speaking Chinese.

00:47.694 --> 00:49.494
Britain isn't growing fast enough.

00:49.496 --> 00:51.730
The Bank of England must do more.

00:51.732 --> 00:55.433
Garbled Speech.

00:55.435 --> 00:58.436
Man Speaking Chinese.

01:00.574 --> 01:03.008
The security
of the international community,

01:03.010 --> 01:05.075
but also acts against...

01:07.581 --> 01:11.183
With implants
to help battlefield injuries.

01:11.185 --> 01:13.952
This makes
simple things like walking much easier...

01:13.954 --> 01:16.354
for troops who have lost a
leg to battlefield injuries.

01:18.225 --> 01:20.025
That both our great nations...

01:20.027 --> 01:22.994
to invoke the wonders of
artificial intelligence...

01:22.996 --> 01:25.730
ensnared on it's terrors.

01:25.732 --> 01:29.734
China's vice
foreign minister is in London for talks.

01:31.471 --> 01:34.105
Great Britain will defend her
allies and her interests...

01:34.107 --> 01:35.907
at home and abroad.

